<note id="fs-id1167065973779" class="learning-objectives"><label/>
<title>Section Learning Objectives</title>
<para id="fs-id1167066057104">By the end of this section, you will be able to do the following:</para><list id="fs-id1167064902426"><item>Explain behaviors of waves, including reflection, refraction, diffraction, interference, and coherence, and describe applications based on these behaviors</item>
<item>Perform calculations related to applications based on wave properties of light</item>
</list></note>

<note id="fs-id1167065938601" class="os-teacher">
<title>Teacher Support</title>
